      <title>伊利诺伊州法官将特朗普从州选票中剔除</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/illinois-judge-removes-trump-from-state-ballot-cnn-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，伊利诺伊州一名法官禁止唐纳德·特朗普参加共和党总统初选，这是第三个因这位前总统在 1 月 6 日美国国会大厦叛乱中所扮演的角色而对其实施此类禁令的州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/illinois-judge-removes-trump-from-state-ballot-cnn-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度莫迪试图推动太空初创企业，缩小与中国的差距</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/india-seeks-new-ways-to-aid-space-startups-close-gap-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的国家太空计划取得了一些令人印象深刻的成就，例如去年首次在月球南极附近着陆，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪本周宣布了 2025 年该国首次载人任务的四名印度宇航员的名单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/india-seeks-new-ways-to-aid-space-startups-close-gap-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称中国民兵在南海的存在有所增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/china-militia-presence-increases-in-south-china-sea-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于华盛顿的亚洲海事透明倡议组织的数据显示，去年，随着北京在地区紧张局势加剧的情况下继续加强其存在，中国在南海主要岛礁周围的海上民兵船只数量增加了35%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/china-militia-presence-increases-in-south-china-sea-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙战争笼罩英国补选，乔治·加洛韦寻求议会复出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/gaza-war-looms-over-rochdale-by-election-with-george-galloway-seeking-comeback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[选民周四将在英格兰西北部举行特别选举，这可能会引发因以色列与哈马斯战争而引发的政治紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/gaza-war-looms-over-rochdale-by-election-with-george-galloway-seeking-comeback</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能已经改变了美国发动战争的方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2024-ai-warfare-project-maven/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国军事人员一开始对人工智能持怀疑态度，但现在他们正在开发并使用 Project Maven 来识别战场上的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2024-ai-warfare-project-maven/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管选举受到谴责，巴基斯坦军队仍牢牢掌握指挥权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/despite-rebuke-in-election-pakistan-s-army-is-still-in-command</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦选民在本月早些时候令人惊讶的选举结果中表达了他们对该国强大军队的失望。但军队仍准备比以往拥有更多的幕后控制权——经济复苏将是其最终考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/despite-rebuke-in-election-pakistan-s-army-is-still-in-command</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大将重新实施签证规则以阻止墨西哥寻求庇护者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/canada-to-reimpose-visa-rules-to-deter-mexican-asylum-seekers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，加拿大将恢复对许多来自墨西哥的旅客的签证要求，以阻止寻求庇护者涌入机场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/canada-to-reimpose-visa-rules-to-deter-mexican-asylum-seekers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 22:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院将权衡特朗普的豁免权，暂停华盛顿特区的审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/supreme-court-to-weigh-trump-immunity-keeps-dc-trial-on-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院表示，将对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 寻求刑事起诉豁免的申请做出裁决，审理这一历史性案件，该案件将决定这位前总统在竞选重返白宫期间是否因干扰 2020 年选举而受审。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/supreme-court-to-weigh-trump-immunity-keeps-dc-trial-on-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 22:03:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国立法者达成协议以避免政府即将关门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/lawmakers-reach-deal-to-avert-us-government-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会领导人在最后一刻达成了一项协议，以避免美国政府造成破坏性关门，这引发了与迅速抨击该协议的极端保守派的另一场冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/lawmakers-reach-deal-to-avert-us-government-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉无视美国斡旋协议，迫使拜登重新实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/venezuela-flouts-us-brokered-deal-pressing-biden-to-reimpose-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉为今年的选举设定了新的条件，无视美国斡旋的协议，并可能引发华盛顿更严厉的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/venezuela-flouts-us-brokered-deal-pressing-biden-to-reimpose-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 18:14:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
